# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>The Capellan Confederation has always relied on its infantry to compensate for the CCAF's chronic shortage of heavier assets. Conventional foot soldiers, drawn from the citizens' militia system that defines Capellan military service, form the backbone of garrison forces across the Confederation's commonalities. CCAF foot platoons anchor the Confederation's garrison network, holding worlds that BattleMech forces cannot permanently occupy. Slow and vulnerable in open terrain, they depend on prepared positions and local knowledge to offset their lack of mobility. These special operations fireteams combine ER Sunbeam Starfire laser rifles with man-portable plasma rifles, pairing precision energy weapons with devastating thermal firepower for high-value target engagement.</p>
</overview>

